            <div id="_j_photo_264674247" data-seq="264674298" data-pid="264674247" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3812">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8045832/264674247.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3F/AE/wKgBZ1oGwA-AdePdAA5uU5Lt5tI14.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3F/AE/wKgBZ1oGwA-AdePdAA5uU5Lt5tI14.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="264674247" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3812.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3812" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>北海公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="264715854">
            《让我们荡起双桨》的创作背景虽然是颐和园的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10807.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="昆明" target="_blank">昆明</a>湖，但我觉得还是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10796.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北海" target="_blank">北海</a>公园更为贴切，“海面倒映着美丽的白塔，四周环绕着绿树红墙”&nbsp;。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_264674248" data-seq="264674299" data-pid="264674248" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3812">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8045832/264674248.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3F/B3/wKgBZ1oGwBaAGmd1AAp4inzBR4A49.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3F/B3/wKgBZ1oGwBaAGmd1AAp4inzBR4A49.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="264674248" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3812.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3812" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>北海公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_264674249" data-seq="264674300" data-pid="264674249" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3812">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8045832/264674249.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3F/B6/wKgBZ1oGwBuAN9CZAAtnEduOfpo73.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3F/B6/wKgBZ1oGwBuAN9CZAAtnEduOfpo73.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="264674249" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3812.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3812" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>北海公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="264716136">
            公园内有很多老人在锻炼，一位老者在打花棍，真是秀得飞起，这些民间技艺应该被广为流传才是，还有抖空竹啊，转手绢啊，让老外知道，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>不是只有广场舞和广播体操。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_264674251" data-seq="264674302" data-pid="264674251" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3812">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8045832/264674251.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3F/B9/wKgBZ1oGwCCAeOY7AAXlprv4abc57.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3F/B9/wKgBZ1oGwCCAeOY7AAXlprv4abc57.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="264674251" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3812.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3812" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>北海公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="264716415">
            <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/186782.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="古北水镇" target="_blank">古北水镇</a>算是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>最新的景点了吧，位于<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13571.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="密云" target="_blank">密云</a>县，于2014年国庆期间正式营业，是仿照<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10434.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="乌镇" target="_blank">乌镇</a>所造的一个旅游休闲度假区。9月份老妈来<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>和我一起办美签，就决定多留几天，让我带她再逛逛09年没去过的地方。<br />
<br />
到达水镇最便捷的交通是在东直门公共交通枢纽站北侧，942、855路公交车场内乘坐直达的旅游巴士，大概两小时直达<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/186782.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="古北水镇" target="_blank">古北水镇</a>。票价：48元/人/单程。也可以报个一日游的团，价格也不贵。水镇门票150元,如果在水镇内规定的酒店留宿，貌似是可以免门票的。如果不赶时间，可以在水镇内留宿一晚，有些酒店自带温泉。<br />
<br />
水镇说大不大，说小不小，毕竟是人造景区，避免不了浓厚的商业气息。主要有司马小烧、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64485.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="永顺" target="_blank">永顺</a>染坊、杨无敌祠、震远镖局等一些列景点。如果是走马观花，不到三小时就可以把水镇走完。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_264674220" data-seq="264674271" data-pid="264674220" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="7731162">
