                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="264748609">
            我对<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/23934.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="江南" target="_blank">江南</a>水乡非常憧憬，一直想去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10434.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="乌镇" target="_blank">乌镇</a>、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10155.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="绍兴" target="_blank">绍兴</a>、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10010.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="西塘" target="_blank">西塘</a>、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10089.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南浔" target="_blank">南浔</a>等古镇旅游。尽管现在的古镇都被严重商业化开发，也还是想去拔个草。原先在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10207.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="苏州" target="_blank">苏州</a>去了七里山塘，这番游<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/186782.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="古北水镇" target="_blank">古北水镇</a>，还是很喜欢在桥梁小巷中穿梭的感觉。
        </p>
