        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8045832/264674227.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:451px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3F/69/wKgBZ1oGv5mAfkAaAA1mNVZEItE37.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3F/69/wKgBZ1oGv5mAfkAaAA1mNVZEItE37.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="264674227" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/7731162.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="7731162" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>古北水镇
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="264753609">
            其实比水镇更有名的，是背后山上的司马台长城。长城门票40，如果和水镇门票一起购买，可以便宜20.上长城的索道往返160，还是很贵的。<br />
<br />
夜游司马台长城是景区的一大特色活动。但在夜游时间段游览，游客能到达的区域较少。司马台长城是长城中最险的一段。长城的最高处为“仙女楼”，需登“天梯”而上。天梯高达100米，坡度85度，几近垂直。而且有几段是没有垛口的，非常危险。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_264674229" data-seq="264674280" data-pid="264674229" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3953">
