            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:451px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3F/7E/wKgBZ1oGv7uAadOiAAnN0xheyUs29.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/3F/7E/wKgBZ1oGv7uAadOiAAnN0xheyUs29.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="264674234" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3953.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3953" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>司马台长城
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="264753690">
            秋季气温渐凉，是登城墙的佳季。长城一侧是静谧的水镇，一侧是祖国的大好河山。傍晚微风习习，随着太阳隐匿在山间，水镇和长城的灯光亮起。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_264674232" data-seq="264674283" data-pid="264674232" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3953">
